Package: Neo4jR
Title: Neo4j Bolt Driver for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A native Neo4j driver for R speaking the Bolt protocol, backed by
    the Rust 'neo4rs' crate via 'extendr'. Connect to a Neo4j database, run
    Cypher statements, and stream results back into data frames without any
    Python or external runtime dependency.
